**Approch:**
***Create a vector of size 26 having all entries as zero
*Run a loop and store frequency of each char freq++  
*Perform sorting and arrange obtain freq in decending order 
*Initiate count with zero value and Maxfreq with value freq[0]
*Run a loop with condition freq[i] > Maxfreq && freq[i]>0 and replace the value with max(0,freq[i]-1)
*In a lop with If condition (freq[i] >Maxfreq satisfied take difference of value of Maxfreq -freq[i]
**

**Example :** 

given string s =  **aaaabbbbccdef**
freq in sorted order are 
freq 4  Maxfreq 4  if condition not satisfy
freq 4  Maxfreq 3 condition satisfy difference is one (4-3) (count=1)
freq 2  Maxfreq 2 if condition not satisfy
freq 1  Maxfreq 1 if condition not satisy 
freq 1  Maxfreq 0 condition satisfy difference is one (1-0) (count=2)
freq 1  Maxfreq 0 condition satisfy difference is one (1-0) (count=3)

return count ,this will give **** Minimum Deletions to Make Character Frequencies Unique**** .

